snippet: The Pakistani military said it killed 28 local and foreign militants in air strikes in the volatile northwest of the country on Sunday, as evidence emerged that civilians had died in previous strikes....

headline.print_headline: Pakistan Military Says 28 Militants Killed in Airstrikes
headline.main: Pakistan Military Says 28 Militants Killed in Airstrikes

lead_paragraph: The Pakistani military said it killed 28 local and foreign militants in air strikes in the volatile northwest of the country on Sunday, as evidence emerged that civilians had died in previous strikes.
